description: Largest unit (1230 square feet) at Channel View Condominium with sweeping ocean/city views in the heart of South Boston with deeded garage parking (heated) and deeded storage locker. Corner unit has an open-concept floor plan and features central air/heat, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, recessed lighting, red oak floors, dovetail cabinetry, laundry room, BainUltra air jet tub and Napoleon gas fireplace. Private master bedroom features an en-suite bathroom with double sinks and walk-in closet. Unit has fantastic views of the Seaport and a private Juliet balcony with recently replaced Andersen French doors. Around the corner from Lincoln, Capo, Loco and Stats.
